### Sunshine Backend — HTTP Client Collection
### Compatible with: JetBrains HTTP Client, VS Code REST Client
###
### Demo seed UUIDs (stable UUID5 — run `python -m app.seeds.demo_seed` first):
###   USER_ID   = 2a307656-dfbb-55f6-9054-007f2014e4a9
###   PLANT_ID  = 23d1867e-f2d0-5bf7-a4c3-f3568c06aeea
###   SPECIES_ID = bc8ce428-d40b-539e-9fbe-f31d002d279c

@base = http://localhost:8000
@user_id = 2a307656-dfbb-55f6-9054-007f2014e4a9
@plant_id = 23d1867e-f2d0-5bf7-a4c3-f3568c06aeea
@species_id = bc8ce428-d40b-539e-9fbe-f31d002d279c
@chat_request_id = 00000000-0000-0000-0028-000000000001
@pest_request_id  = 00000000-0000-0000-0028-000000000002
@companion_request_id = 00000000-0000-0000-0028-000000000003


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Liveness probe
GET {{base}}/healthz

###

### Readiness probe (checks Postgres)
GET {{base}}/readyz

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLANTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List plants for demo user (header auth)
GET {{base}}/plants
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###

### Get plant detail — 초록이
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###

### Get plant detail — query param auth (fallback)
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}?user_id={{user_id}}

###

### Get home screen card for plant
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/card
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###

### Species candidates (classifier mock)
POST {{base}}/plants/species-candidates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "image_ref": "uploads/demo-leaf.jpg",
  "locale": "ko-KR",
  "top_k": 3
}

###

### Create a new plant (returns plant_id — use in subsequent requests)
POST {{base}}/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "species_profile_id": "{{species_id}}",
  "nickname": "새싹이",
  "room_name": "침실"
}

###

### Update character state (internal / dev)
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/character-state
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "condition": "needs_water"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HOME
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Home screen — all plant summary cards
GET {{base}}/home
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SENSOR READINGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Inject soil moisture reading (below threshold → triggers watering rule)
POST {{base}}/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "metric": "soil_moisture_pct",
  "value": 18.5,
  "recorded_at": "2026-05-11T09:00:00Z"
}

###

### Inject light reading
POST {{base}}/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "metric": "light_lux",
  "value": 850.0,
  "recorded_at": "2026-05-11T09:00:00Z"
}

###

### Inject humidity reading
POST {{base}}/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "metric": "humidity_pct",
  "value": 55.0,
  "recorded_at": "2026-05-11T09:00:00Z"
}

###

### Inject temperature reading
POST {{base}}/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "metric": "temperature_c",
  "value": 22.5,
  "recorded_at": "2026-05-11T09:00:00Z"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ENVIRONMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Environment snapshot + character explanation
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/environment
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CARE LOGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Log a watering action (also updates character state)
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/care-logs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "action_type": "watering",
  "acted_at": "2026-05-11T08:30:00Z"
}

###

### Log a note
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/care-logs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "action_type": "note",
  "note": "새 잎이 나오기 시작했어요.",
  "acted_at": "2026-05-11T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### List care logs (newest first)
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/care-logs
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INTERNAL — Rule Engine Sync
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Trigger rule engine sync (dev only — not public API)
POST {{base}}/internal/rule-character-sync/{{plant_id}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CHAT — Intent Classification
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Classify question intent only (no LLM answer)
POST {{base}}/chat/intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_id": "{{chat_request_id}}",
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라에 물을 얼마나 자주 줘야 해?"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CHAT — Full Pipeline (RAG + LLM)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Chat: watering question (full pipeline)
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "request_id": "{{chat_request_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라에 물을 얼마나 자주 줘야 해?"
}

###

### Chat: replay same request_id → from_cache: true
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "request_id": "{{chat_request_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라에 물을 얼마나 자주 줘야 해?"
}

###

### Chat: pest reference question (guardrail — is_reference_only: true)
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "request_id": "{{pest_request_id}}",
  "question": "잎에 점이 생겼는데 병충해인가요?"
}

###

### Chat: companion plant intent
POST {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "request_id": "{{companion_request_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라와 함께 키우면 좋은 식물은 뭐가 있어?"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# COMPANION RECOMMENDATIONS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Companion plant recommendations for 초록이
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/companion-recommendations
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###

### With custom top_k
GET {{base}}/plants/{{plant_id}}/companion-recommendations?top_k=10
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RETRIEVAL (low-level — for testing)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Hybrid retrieval query
POST {{base}}/retrieval/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0028-000000000010",
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라 물주기 주기",
  "top_k": 5
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EVIDENCE (internal — for testing)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Build evidence bundle
POST {{base}}/evidence/build
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plant_id": "{{plant_id}}",
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "question": "몬스테라에 물을 얼마나 자주 줘야 해?",
  "intent": "watering_question"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUDIT — Chat Run Evidence
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Full decision audit for the watering chat run
GET {{base}}/chat-runs/{{chat_request_id}}/evidence

###

### Full decision audit for the pest guardrail run
GET {{base}}/chat-runs/{{pest_request_id}}/evidence

###
